Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那麼，那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.40,0:00:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有沒有隱瞞真實身份做過什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.60,0:00:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是不得以而為之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.60,0:00:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無論如何要說出自己真實的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.30,0:00:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了自己的感受，為了重要的朋友們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了想要守護的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.00,0:00:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐，我理解你的心情！心情！心情！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.20,0:02:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.90,0:03:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你們，我們遊樂園的生意越來越紅火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這代表了我真誠的謝意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡情享用這頓晚餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.40,0:03:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不客氣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.40,0:03:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆為人這麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.10,0:03:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是人不可貌相啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.40,0:03:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是給我們打預防針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我們以後要更賣力的表演是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是洛吉特，是這樣就最好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太直白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.40,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，好像沒有看見面具明星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.40,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她……她今天要去練習鎖鏈鐮刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖鏈鐮刀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.70,0:03:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？那真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人給您送花來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.80,0:04:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有些影迷\N不知道您現在應該在倫敦才送來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.10,0:04:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由利送的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙面演出很開心嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐，請快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.60,0:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒乘上6點的班機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.80,0:04:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會趕不上明天下午的拍攝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發給您的電子郵件應該已經看過了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個照片裏的面具明星就是蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉現在正在倫敦拍電影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.40,0:04:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不可能是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.00,0:04:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是聽說新生的卡萊多劇團的顧客數量銳減
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形勢很是不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要再做那些不入流的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.70,0:04:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，事實真相很快就會明朗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上即將到達倫敦西斯羅機場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.70,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CUT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了，蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那段我想檢查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來倫敦有公事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.70,0:06:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，一直想著要來拍攝現場看你一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好趕巧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.00,0:06:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是擔心你的\N可愛的女兒會不會遇到什麼麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.60,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你調教的越來越好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，你們慢慢聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.90,0:06:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有無聊的謠言說你在遊樂園露面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是由利•凱力亞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.00,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些無聊的小人的謠言，不用理他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天迪奧休息？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.00,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去參加西雅圖巡迴馬戲團的日場演出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能繼續在屋頂上演出了，老天不做美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.70,0:07:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果今天下一天雨的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不是就能有個難得的休息日了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要總結目前為止的問題以及排練今後的新動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，舞臺都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細的日程安排我回頭再和你細談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.90,0:07:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為\N我們的關係打亂了你的演出行程？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.60,0:07:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的日程都是按照我的意願安排的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.60,0:07:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題啦，哪邊我都會安排好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.10,0:07:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.80,0:07:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想買下一天2000張門票？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.10,0:07:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想作為禮物送給來卡萊多劇團光顧的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.70,0:08:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是1天2000張門票的三個月份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.10,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共18萬張門票一次付清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18萬張？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月好象會不停的下雨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.70,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來似乎會被天氣影響\N客流量不僅僅我們園的專利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.70,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您既然說了就是筆生意了，那麼條件呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，不過很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.40,0:08:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你停止FREEDOMRIZE的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們現在是我們遊樂園的搖錢樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能這麼輕易就放棄她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是不算面具明星在內呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.50,0:08:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可能再也不會出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍攝順利是首要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.50,0:09:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部電影是否成功對你將來的影響非常大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此才精心挑選劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.50,0:09:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招募最優秀的製片人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.80,0:09:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週末影片將進入最高潮的拍攝期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預祝你成功，蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.80,0:09:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.50,0:09:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.90,0:10:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具明星沒有出現？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓由利說對了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.90,0:10:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解雇我們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，這和合同不符啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是我要說的，不明白嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.40,0:10:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具明星居然不是你們的正式成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.50,0:10:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是嚴重違反合同內容的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.10,0:10:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，還好由利•凱力亞告訴我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.40,0:10:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由利？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.50,0:10:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，你們快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.60,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利這個傢伙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.90,0:10:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底想把我們逼到什麼地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.20,0:10:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說最近卡萊多劇團的生意不怎麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我們妨礙了他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.00,0:10:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.10,0:10:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是托他的福，我明白了件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.90,0:10:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.00,0:10:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我們在某些地方做的還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以後怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.60,0:11:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道還要回去過打工生活？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.20,0:11:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，那個或許可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.50,0:11:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫哥華國際表演大賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.20,0:11:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，去年及前年我就是因此而得到合約的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.30,0:11:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.50,0:11:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這裏得到好評
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.80,0:11:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬林遊樂園的老闆會重新考慮也說不定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，預賽的時間就要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.10,0:11:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得以你們的實力預賽應該沒有問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很期待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.20,0:11:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特太厲害啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.30,0:11:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是大人物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在敵人面前就能讓他們害怕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，叫大家一起來練習吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔術師的逆位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.70,0:12:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.70,0:12:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？根本沒有讓那些人參加比賽的必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.40,0:12:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓她們來破壞\N我作為特別評委參加的表演大賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.40,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦不，等下，說不定她們還不知道我是評委呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，讓她們參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說她們丟了\N瑪林遊樂園的那份工作都是由利在搞的鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，應該是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.20,0:12:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我稍微調查了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.10,0:13:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天FREEDOMRIZE那些人\N報名參加了溫哥華國家表演大賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個爸爸為了準備和新星簽約的選拔賽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.60,0:13:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，由利•凱力亞還被選為特邀評委
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有不好的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.00,0:13:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三藩市的班機都取消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.20,0:13:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添了很多麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不啊，我是小姐的支持者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.20,0:13:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油拍電影吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.50,0:13:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.00,0:13:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個溫哥華國際表演大賽什麼時候舉行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.70,0:13:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個週末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個週末……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.00,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週末影片將進入最高潮的拍攝期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我最好的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.10,0:13:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的誇獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.30,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.90,0:14:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有新動靜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.70,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由表演團體Z突然報名參加比賽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.80,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z應該是那個在街頭表演的小組吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.60,0:14:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，街頭表演小組有特別允許才能參加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.10,0:14:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起我注意的是他們預定的\N表演內容和FREEDOMRIZE十分相象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CUT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.40,0:14:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，請再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.70,0:14:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去辦事處打聽過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.60,0:14:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報名參賽的人數和現場登臺的人數沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這……這算什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.60,0:14:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.90,0:15:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫哥華雜技表演小組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.50,0:15:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演的內容和我們的簡直一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算自己退出了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被這麼可怕的目光注視著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是這次大賽的評委
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.30,0:15:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z是溫哥華本地街頭表演小組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為評委有責任推薦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.40,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給有能力的人們些機會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你們對自己的表演充滿自信就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況對手是街頭表演小組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不可能輸給街頭表演小組吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.80,0:16:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個登場的是本地雜技表演小組Z
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很受歡迎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.60,0:16:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.20,0:16:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們的不是一模一樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.50,0:16:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盜取了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.80,0:16:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還被修改了許多，演技顯得更華麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.30,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媒體將會宣傳是\NFREEDOMRIZE擅自盜取Z的表演內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.90,0:16:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才能阻止這棵好苗苗的成長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有意思啊，值得試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.90,0:17:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的好的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.30,0:17:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以特別允許你們加入卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是比較喜歡自由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.00,0:17:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成得太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能夠向這種傢伙認輸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.80,0:17:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.50,0:17:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍攝的事就延遲到下周
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相應的我期待你的最佳表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.50,0:18:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下麵登場的是來自NA的FREEDOMRIZE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具明星？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在幹什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利！謝謝你的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來妨礙我的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.50,0:19:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.10,0:19:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……到底那組的表演更好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.80,0:19:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉•哈姆雷特現在已經不是專業演員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此她們失去參賽資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.60,0:20:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天應該是拍攝影片的高潮幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經申請延期拍攝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.20,0:20:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我這麼做很任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不能不這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.30,0:20:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.50,0:20:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不明白你在想些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.10,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.40,0:20:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾下定決心一定要只做讓爸爸高興的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.80,0:20:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有這次我不能夠阻止自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.50,0:20:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的這些夥伴對我來說是多麼的重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.40,0:20:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我發現我還有沒有完成的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.40,0:21:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想完整地……完整地演出場燃盡熱情的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.70,0:21:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想揮灑身體中更多激情的汗水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.80,0:21:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在對我來說就是她們的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.80,0:21:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.30,0:21:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有表演我的最後一場演出呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.20,0:21:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之，影片一定要拍完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.50,0:21:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就隨你便吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.90,0:21:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.50,0:21:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天的表演怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸……可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.50,0:21:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用去追嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天他會明白我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.60,0:21:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.30,0:22:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.50,0:22:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見我了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.00,0:22:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.30,0:22:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說真能夠完成那種演技？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.10,0:22:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事，蕾拉小姐能看見夫魯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.40,0:22:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.30,0:22:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻的超絕技？很不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.50,0:22:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過到底要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.90,0:22:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於擺脫過去的自縛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.70,0:22:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯開始打破常規的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.80,0:22:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻超絕技的全貌是？！是？！是？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.70,0:22:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.60,0:22:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀是夢想，飛向空
